  "3133310": {
    "name": "Jackal Demo",
    "steam_appid": 3133310,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>你是一个在罪恶之城地下世界横行无忌的嗑药毁灭机器。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无需潜行。无需躲藏。只需像个超人般的破坏球，横扫整个犯罪家族。掠夺他们的金库。夺取他们的女人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黑帮建造了拉斯维加斯。<strong>你将把它撕成碎片。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133310/extras/3c94de68fc4cf1ae4250f5a76a038dcf.poster.avif?t=1770279808\" width=1170 height=532 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133310/extras/3c94de68fc4cf1ae4250f5a76a038dcf.webm?t=1770279808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133310/extras/3c94de68fc4cf1ae4250f5a76a038dcf.mp4?t=1770279808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>从沙发到霰弹枪——一切皆可为武器</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身为嗑药版约翰·威克，将拉斯维加斯变成即兴杀戮的舞台。<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133310/extras/b50d8bb7a6201b82c969e64736140093.poster.avif?t=1770279808\" width=1170 height=532 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133310/extras/b50d8bb7a6201b82c969e64736140093.webm?t=1770279808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133310/extras/b50d8bb7a6201b82c969e64736140093.mp4?t=1770279808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>每个终结技都是一笔画。</strong> <strong>每个房间都是杀戮的盛宴。</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快过思考。强过任何持枪的黑帮分子。换弹只会拖慢你的脚步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为<strong>不可阻挡</strong>的存在。不死不灭。无人能敌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133310/extras/6cccf74c377e61e98f7996876f7612a7.poster.avif?t=1770279808\" width=1170 height=532 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133310/extras/6cccf74c377e61e98f7996876f7612a7.webm?t=1770279808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133310/extras/6cccf74c377e61e98f7996876f7612a7.mp4?t=1770279808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>没有两次屠杀是相同的</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次突袭都与众不同，包含：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 可解锁的毒品超能力</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随机生成的房间</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可叠加的游戏玩法调节器</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一系列残酷的终结技</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各种敌人类型</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >标志性的拉斯维加斯地点</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >标志性的70年代武器</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武器化的物品，助燃无尽的创意暴力</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133310/extras/dcfbd5687c77bf3724d902e9f4f9a061.poster.avif?t=1770279808\" width=780 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133310/extras/dcfbd5687c77bf3724d902e9f4f9a061.webm?t=1770279808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133310/extras/dcfbd5687c77bf3724d902e9f4f9a061.mp4?t=1770279808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>迷幻药版《好家伙》。当黑帮经典遇上致幻剂</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >回到那个烟雾缭绕的房间、迷幻爵士乐和不道德仍是时尚的年代。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在迷幻黑色故事中，一个杀手和他的超自然伙伴在70年代被黑帮控制的拉斯维加斯中穿行，每个清理工作都渗透到下一个，现实只是另一场糟糕的致幻之旅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >买票上车，开始这趟旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133310/extras/2e53c33b91ae57c623d5873d19f6f2fb.poster.avif?t=1770279808\" width=1170 height=532 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133310/extras/2e53c33b91ae57c623d5873d19f6f2fb.webm?t=1770279808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133310/extras/2e53c33b91ae57c623d5873d19f6f2fb.mp4?t=1770279808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>由马修·柯蒂斯配音（《I Am Your Beast》）</i></strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>由米哈尔·马钦科夫斯基制作（《Soldat》、《Maniac》、《Butcher》）</strong></i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>灵感来源：《热线迈阿密》、《OTXO》、《I Am Your Beast》、《疾速追杀》、《低俗小说》、《拉斯维加斯的恐惧与厌恶》、《好家伙》、《星际牛仔》</i></strong></p></li></ul>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 阿拉伯语, 保加利亚语, 捷克语, 丹麦语, 荷兰语, 芬兰语, 希腊语, 匈牙利语, 印度尼西亚语, 日语, 韩语, 挪威语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 罗马尼亚语, 俄语, 简体中文, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 瑞典语, 泰语, 繁体中文, 土耳其语, 乌克兰语, 越南语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
